### Workflow API Test Suite
### Based on Diagrid Catalyst Workflow Quickstart
### https://docs.diagrid.io/catalyst/quickstart/workflow

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5001/

###

### Start Workflow
// @name startWorkflow
POST http://localhost:5001/workflow/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Car",
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### Get Workflow Status
### Uses the workflow ID from the previous start request
@instanceId={{startWorkflow.response.body.instanceId}}
GET http://localhost:5001/workflow/status/{{instanceId}}

###

### Terminate Workflow
### Uses the workflow ID from the previous start request

@instanceId={{startWorkflow.response.body.instanceId}}
POST http://localhost:5001/workflow/terminate/{{instanceId}}
